            <p class="comment-content">加深了对近代史上各家军阀之了解。虽然是一篇篇的评论式小文，但对于未曾了解过这段历史的同学来说，确实比较有味道。故事短小、别开生面、论述精彩、值得一看。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1151858272">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-1151858272" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-1151858272" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="1151858272">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/zy2light/">圆，抑或是方</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2017-02-13</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">嬉笑怒骂，信手拈来，畅快，畅快啊</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="1095585593">
